    Still in the ship, under lock, key, and force feild, Black Aracnia 
watches Quickstrike and Darkmouse make there way through the ship. 
Unfortunetly, for them, in a moment they would be dead because the internal 
Autoguns were coming online.
    She activated the ships PA system, "Attention Quickstrike and Darkmouse. 
This is Black Aracnia, the temporary Predacon Commander. You are trapped 
inside the ship. All doorways, corriodrs, and shafts are closed. The internal 
defences have been initiated, and if you try to move from your current 
position you will be shot. I suggest you surrender now, or I will release 
Nerve gas into your section of the ship. Understood?"
